{"id":"c2m-j2s","title":"MVP Integration — Live Telemetry Pipeline","description":"Wire everything together: PM5 → BLE → BleakPm5Adapter → MQTT. Workout lifecycle detection (start/end/pause/resume state machine from notification data). Live telemetry publishing (aggregated state QoS 0, per-stroke QoS 0). Health \u0026 availability (cosalette health, LWT, retained availability messages). End-to-end validation on real PM5 hardware. Covers features F1-F7.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","owner":"mail@fabiankoerner.com","created_at":"2026-03-07T14:27:51Z","created_by":"Fabian Koerner","updated_at":"2026-04-18T07:33:48Z","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":0,"comment_count":0}
