{"id":"c2m-1am","title":"Convert assert! to Result in proprietary command encoders","description":"Seven assert!() calls in proprietary.rs guard Vec\u003cu8\u003e payload lengths (LocalRaceParticipant, AuthenPassword, CableTest, RaceParticipant, LogCardMemory, DisplayString, DisplayBitmap). These panic on oversized input, which from Python surfaces as PanicException. Convert to Result\u003c(), EncodeError\u003e and propagate through encode() so PyO3 wrappers return PyResult\u003cVec\u003cu8\u003e\u003e with clean ValueError messages. Add edge-case tests for oversized inputs.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","owner":"mail@fabiankoerner.com","created_at":"2026-03-11T22:25:48Z","created_by":"Fabian Koerner","updated_at":"2026-04-18T07:33:48Z","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":0,"comment_count":0}
